metadata.description:
This is the NFT of the original art work created by the resin artist at The Art Genie - https://instagram.com/the_artgenie?igshid=Mzc1MmZhNjY=

Please feel free to DM via Instagram if you wish to purchase the original art piece.

Once you purchase the digital NFT you would be eligible for 15% discount on original artwork.

Thanks and Cheers !
